    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322540/extras/a4a97b8623ed8721cd5c510a78ccc590.poster.avif?t=1741879992\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322540/extras/a4a97b8623ed8721cd5c510a78ccc590.webm?t=1741879992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322540/extras/a4a97b8623ed8721cd5c510a78ccc590.mp4?t=1741879992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一辆开往郊区的公交车，瞬间化为炼狱。爆炸的冲击波撕裂了宁静，十条生命戛然而止。现场一片狼藉，仅剩残骸与谜团。林山海带领现场勘察组进行细致勘察并走访了所有死者家属和好友，案情仍然毫无头绪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322540/extras/73a957e8abb91eb386df689788dab8ab.avif?t=1741879992\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322540/extras/8e4989704bcad680491bd440fdd94180.poster.avif?t=1741879992\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322540/extras/8e4989704bcad680491bd440fdd94180.webm?t=1741879992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322540/extras/8e4989704bcad680491bd440fdd94180.mp4?t=1741879992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真相隐藏在爆炸前那关键的十分钟里。你将置身于时间的漩涡，一次又一次地重返案发现场，以第一视角体验那最后的时刻。通过细致的观察和严密的推理，将散落的线索拼接成完整的拼图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322540/extras/dd80061dbefc0f2f43c90a845dea9665.avif?t=1741879992\" width=616 height=550 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322540/extras/39432118e1d1eb181fc5cb74dade4e77.poster.avif?t=1741879992\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322540/extras/39432118e1d1eb181fc5cb74dade4e77.webm?t=1741879992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322540/extras/39432118e1d1eb181fc5cb74dade4e77.mp4?t=1741879992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不是一场简单的解谜游戏，而是一场与时间赛跑的推理挑战。你需要在脑海中构建错综复杂的线索网络，运用演绎推理，抽丝剥茧，最终锁定真凶。每一次推理都是一次冒险，每一个细节都可能成为破案的关键。你能否在时间耗尽之前，揭开迷雾，将凶手绳之以法？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322540/extras/881556fba2c1fd36b6d17d2bc88f007e.avif?t=1741879992\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家首先需要在案发现场搜证线索，然后在脑图中推理合并线索，最终抵达真相。您可以根据线索雷达的提示，来寻找物证，遇到拿不准的线索时，可以使用线索分析仪来辅助推理。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322540/extras/69bd67162488830e907ab0d5eee9a9e8.avif?t=1741879992\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩家Q群</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >0号:676614585<br>1号:606830488 <br>2号:1076610940 <br>3号:736747955</p>",
